data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!  This modern, move-in ready home sits on a highly desirable almost quarter-acre lot. Upon entrance, you are greeted by an abundance of natural light and beautiful laminate wood floors. Make your way into the kitchen where you will find both a beautiful island and all of your Samsung stainless steel appliances. The floorplan opens up seamlessly into your spacious dining room with access to the sliding glass door opening up to the backyard. The main-level primary bedroom is accompanied by a private, 4-piece en-suite bathroom complete with a luxury feeling walk-in shower. With one standard and one walk-in closet, you will have plenty of room for storage. The vaulted ceilings greet you in the living room to a comfortable, convenient space that is great for entertaining or relaxation. Make your way upstairs to the other two bedrooms and another full bathroom. This home is a must-see! Schedule your showing today!
